---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Free Modern Creative Stuff" description="Learn about our mission to bring you the best free creative resources">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #667eea;">About Us</h1>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">Our Mission</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
          Welcome to Free Modern Creative Stuff! We're dedicated to bringing you the finest collection of fonts,
          graphics, and design resources from Creative Fabrica. Our mission is to make high-quality creative
          assets accessible to everyone, whether you're a professional designer or just starting your creative journey.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">What We Offer</h2>
        <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 24px;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Modern Fonts:</strong> Discover unique, handcrafted fonts perfect for any project</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Graphics & Illustrations:</strong> Beautiful designs for all your creative needs</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Quality Curated:</strong> Every resource is carefully selected for quality and uniqueness</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Free Access:</strong> All resources are available through our Creative Fabrica partnership</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">Our Partnership</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
          We're proud partners with <a href="https://www.creativefabrica.com/ref/16577150/" style="color: #f5576c; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Creative Fabrica</a>,
          one of the world's leading platforms for creative resources. Through this partnership, we can offer you
          access to thousands of premium fonts, graphics, and design assets.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">Get Started</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          Browse our collection, find something you love, and click "Get it for free" to access it on Creative Fabrica.
          It's that simple!
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Explore Resources</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
